{"tid":555370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啲厹成撚日chur啲女出街真係好撚戇鳩","createTime":"2018-02-09T11:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T21:44:33.000Z","uid":30859,"like":10,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"43e6bbb85a3bf9e34a7146b2b3b3ae6e26e3abeb","tid":555370,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱有個女性朋友同我呻<br />\n隻厹日撚日都問佢幾時出街<br />\n之前怕鳩咗隻厹都出過次<br />\n出完嗰晚已經問下次幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚好笑係平時隻厹都叫我個女性朋友一齊打壁球<br />\n我朋友唔想又廢事傷佢心咪話搵日先囉<br />\n佢一俾隻厹知會同其他人打壁球就問做乜鳩唔叫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌又唔係識佢啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都唔止一個<br />\n依個世界嘅厹真係好猖狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好撚好笑好心人地成日都話唔得閒就自己收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁chur人真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffd6c209f6f07d7b9e77548f64cd52a8d99a004","tid":555370,"uid":65256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"幾時同我出街"},{"pid":"3ae6468a1248e930b139891f2f7a4ee0184131d9","tid":555370,"uid":78622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ffd6c209f6f07d7b9e77548f64cd52a8d99a004","tid":555370,"uid":65256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"幾時同我出街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"我同你出"},{"pid":"afe518650b2d9ad82a35436919734f9f3bfffaf4","tid":555370,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae6468a1248e930b139891f2f7a4ee0184131d9","tid":555370,"uid":78622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ffd6c209f6